  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| Developer's Note ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've always learned to make games by making games, and love making small, solid arcade games with simple mechanics. <strong>Expect 'X-teroids' to be a small, replayable arcade high-scoring game whose sole goal is to survive the game for 10 minutes while accumulating scores and unlocking a few extra skins.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I appreciate the feedback and will do everything I can to ensure support for my game. If you experience problems with the game, please leave a review on the store page, or if you just want to say hello, please contact me via email.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you for taking the time to read this article; I really hope you enjoy playing my game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>liangxie - Team SunnyTech</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| GAMEPLAY ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"X-teroids\" improves upon the original \"Asteroids\" game by adding features tailored to modern players. With just a mouse or joystick directional buttons, players can freely control their spaceship, but of course, skillful operation requires practice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| Feature ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, several unique props can constitute emergent experiences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/518e0bada2fdf6c252b166febff8bc2a.poster.avif?t=1740208951\" width=800 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/518e0bada2fdf6c252b166febff8bc2a.webm?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/518e0bada2fdf6c252b166febff8bc2a.mp4?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/059d69b4cd99e99df2e5e396ff32b999.poster.avif?t=1740208951\" width=692 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/059d69b4cd99e99df2e5e396ff32b999.webm?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/059d69b4cd99e99df2e5e396ff32b999.mp4?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/ecd290c24a12abfb0b6d81ca65d0f3f4.poster.avif?t=1740208951\" width=692 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/ecd290c24a12abfb0b6d81ca65d0f3f4.webm?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/ecd290c24a12abfb0b6d81ca65d0f3f4.mp4?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break your own records by consistently setting new personal bests. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with your friends on the friend leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/ab652826c0b3aa528925488e05df7956.avif?t=1740208951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras_big/ab652826c0b3aa528925488e05df7956.avif?t=1740208951 width=800 height=538 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your place on the global leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/5e4a2596fe3991d6080a7ffae45f2915.avif?t=1740208951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras_big/5e4a2596fe3991d6080a7ffae45f2915.avif?t=1740208951 width=800 height=538 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the black and white theme, two themes are also supported</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/8bf5745dfb8e2f0a7480ad277e02547d.avif?t=1740208951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras_big/8bf5745dfb8e2f0a7480ad277e02547d.avif?t=1740208951 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/6d1e849124309a8f2c43bc7f1af3a571.avif?t=1740208951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras_big/6d1e849124309a8f2c43bc7f1af3a571.avif?t=1740208951 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >English and chinese language supported</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| Developer's Note ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've always learned to make games by making games, and love making small, solid arcade games with simple mechanics. <strong>Expect 'X-teroids' to be a small, replayable arcade high-scoring game whose sole goal is to survive the game for 10 minutes while accumulating scores and unlocking a few extra skins.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I appreciate the feedback and will do everything I can to ensure support for my game. If you experience problems with the game, please leave a review on the store page, or if you just want to say hello, please contact me via email.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you for taking the time to read this article; I really hope you enjoy playing my game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>liangxie - Team SunnyTech</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| GAMEPLAY ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"X-teroids\" improves upon the original \"Asteroids\" game by adding features tailored to modern players. With just a mouse or joystick directional buttons, players can freely control their spaceship, but of course, skillful operation requires practice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|||||||||| Feature ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, several unique props can constitute emergent experiences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/518e0bada2fdf6c252b166febff8bc2a.poster.avif?t=1740208951\" width=800 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/518e0bada2fdf6c252b166febff8bc2a.webm?t=1740208951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"